Module no.ntnu.idatt1002
Package no.ntnu.idatt1002.data

Class Group

java.lang.Object
no.ntnu.idatt1002.data.Group
public final class Group extends Object
This class represents a group of users. Each group has a unique ID, but not necessarily a unique name.
